	<article class="post-644569 post type-post status-publish hentry category-mergers-acquisitions category-telecommunications tag-3-uk tag-cellular-telephones tag-europe tag-great-britain tag-hutchison-whampoa-limited tag-li-ka-shing tag-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures tag-telefonica-europe-plc tag-telefonica-sa tag-telefonica-uk-ltd tag-telephones-and-telecommunications tag-vodafone-group-plc tag-wireless-communications per-li-ka-shing des-cellular-telephones des-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures des-telephones-and-telecommunications des-wireless-communications org-3-uk org-hutchison-whampoa-limited org-telefonica-europe-plc org-telefonica-sa org-telefonica-uk-ltd org-vodafone-group-plc geo-europe geo-great-britain news_keywords-3-uk news_keywords-europe news_keywords-great-britain news_keywords-li-ka-shing-2 news_keywords-mergers-and-acquistions news_keywords-mobile-phone news_keywords-o2 news_keywords-o2telefonica-uk-ltd news_keywords-telecommunication news_keywords-wireless-2" id="post-644569">
